  "title": "Assistant Store Manager",
  "description": "<p>As the Assistant Store Manager, you will <strong>support the Store Manager in driving sales, maximising store profitability, and delivering high-quality customer service</strong>. You will help ensure the store <strong>meets KPIs</strong>, <strong>maintains company standards</strong>, and <strong>represents the brand professionally</strong>.<br /></p><p><strong>Customer Service</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Deliver first-class customer service</strong> and support customer retention</p></li><li><p><strong>Handle customer enquiries and complaints</strong> effectively</p></li><li><p><strong>Drive service consistency</strong> across the store team</p></li></ul><p><strong>Sales</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Support the achievement and exceeding of sales targets</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Analyse sales and trade reports</strong> (e.g. Oracle, Trade Review) to support performance decisions</p></li><li><p><strong>Maximise sales opportunities</strong> through effective use of in-store devices</p></li></ul><p><strong>Visual Merchandising</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Execute weekly visual merchandising briefs</strong> and maintain visual standards</p></li><li><p><strong>Ensure products, displays, and windows</strong> meet visual merchandising guidelines</p></li></ul><p><strong>Training & Development</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Support team development and training</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Track team progression and completion of required E-Assessments</strong></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p><strong>Minimum 5 years’ experience</strong> in fast-paced retail with supervisory exposure</p></li><li><p><strong>Sales-driven and results-oriented</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Able to work independently</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Strong leadership and problem-solving skills</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Location : ION & VIVO</strong></p></li></ul><p><br />Lee Pei Fang Felicia<br />People Profilers Pte Ltd<br />20 Cecil Street, #08-09, PLUS Building, Singapore 049705<br />www.peopleprofilers.com<br />EA License Number: 02C4944<br />EA Personnel Reg no: R22109421</p>",
